{"tid":1374003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈2019秋冬時尚 係 頭盔 護甲 豬嘴！！！！！ pantone係黑色！！！","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:00:38.000Z","uid":105976,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49685e8075b1951032a31ab73e346ae3688ebab5","tid":1374003,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"而家個個驚俾人周到有防具會俾黑警針對  走果時丟晒d裝  <br />\n<br />\n之前咪有post話 外國人好支持hk人 但唔知點幫   <br />\n<br />\n機會黎啦飛雲<br />\n解決方法就係將防具變時尚   無論hk/外國 平時成街都係防具    <br />\n<br />\n咩armani. 咩coco channel.  今季時尚展加入頭盔 護甲 豬嘴  鬼佬氣候咁乾爽要支持簡單啦 <br />\n<br />\n到時候俾黑警問  譽佢： 咩示威者？阿蛇你唔係唔識嘛 2019秋冬新裝阿！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n好多護甲頭盔其實真心好型  大家一齊研究下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hBuazu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hBuazu.jpg&h=c20ef91d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"718b5190c733c1a8df54b4c7064ae7b6509cda15","tid":1374003,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"hk路邊空氣... 用豬嘴其實好合理"},{"pid":"955292d8b940dc89ec312f3f95ef6d34b7ace9ca","tid":1374003,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"溝通問題成為每一次打機嘅問大問題，到底點先可以令前排坦克同後排輔助可以溝通到呢？<br />\n<br />\n諗咗陣，發覺可以用顏色旗黎做訊號<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">前進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">停留</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">退守</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［建議］ 前後排溝通方案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373927\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373927</a>"},{"pid":"a75b7f6375bdc564d2b76e77481a05a7ca9a3fed","tid":1374003,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f4c833af31e1ad696b7920aaf0ad22bf41